<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_846c42c4-3931-45ef-9fca-1ec26c0239ed" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>C1P6</sptc><title id="_463df671-71c6-43f2-860f-02bd12f88397">Contamination</title><archive-num>2019: CP1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_5f3f1d12-32a5-4281-88ea-34ede116b5ff" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8201cc80-c269-4ab7-84bf-8618081042eb">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The entry of water, foul gases, sewerage and sullage from a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_83166268-b937-4262-9f45-565c411674fa" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> system into buildings must be avoided.</p></subclause><subclause id="_074ff1de-dcbd-489e-a377-49685d36e7ba" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_69c213bb-05e7-4f7f-8328-77f9d411d341">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The entry of foul gases from a sanitary plumbing system into buildings must be avoided, such that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_0214d816-f8ca-463f-b7d9-fcc6a2bcbe7f">at pressures of up to ±375 Pa, water trap seals will not be reduced to depths less than<ol><li>70 mm for trap seals in pressurised rooms; and</li><li>25 mm for all other applications; or</li></ol></li><li id="_6b53d2dd-0fba-48a6-90de-af1cbb5e0567">an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1260_2.0.0.xml#_6a914e67-bc6e-4499-8316-001bc4729a09" id="_50503bad-88fa-4990-b3e0-ca3eac0d4714" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">equivalent</xref> level of safety to human health is achieved as a system complying with (a).</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_ad645141-1ce0-41db-b81f-1ae9857eb7fa" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b67ed59d-834c-4338-90e7-ea3bbf81445b">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>The entry of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1486_26.7.0.xml#_02c3900f-c9bb-470b-93f4-d71555f2fea7" id="_8b28051c-c429-44c2-891e-8b0f856fdb01" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">surface water</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/9502_0.6.0.xml#_49fcb971-d792-44ac-af74-6243aa2b5b23" id="_3eb8ef4c-42ac-4150-9bdb-68e5b47be36a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sub-surface water</xref> and stormwater into a sanitary plumbing system must be avoided.</p></subclause></clause>